莎朗·斯通声称医生认为她“假装”脑出血https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-claims-doctors-thought-she-was-faking-brain-haemorrhage-3523615?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sharon-stone-claims-doctors-以为她假装脑出血Elizabeth AubreyFri, 27 Oct 2023 10:04:18 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3523615 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎朗·斯通" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “如果他们把我送回家，我就会死”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-claims-doctors-thought-she-was-faking-brain-haemorrhage-3523615">莎朗·斯通声称医生认为她“假装”脑出血的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎朗·斯通" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-red-carpet-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-stone">莎朗·斯通</a>声称医生认为她“伪造”了 2001 年的脑溢血。</p><p>那一年，斯通中风导致脑部出血，并持续了九天，因此入院治疗。事件发生后，这位<em>《本能》</em>明星的生存机会只有百分之一。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.vogue.co.uk/article/sharon-stone-disability" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Vogue》</em></a>杂志最新采访时，斯通回忆起自己在洛杉矶医院醒来时感到剧烈头痛。</p><p> “我记得在轮床上醒来，问那个推着轮床的孩子我要去哪里，他说，‘脑部手术’，”这位女演员说。</p><p> “一名医生在我不知情或未同意的情况下决定对我进行探索性脑部手术，并将我送往手术室。我从这次经历中学到的是，在医疗环境中，女性的声音常常被忽视，特别是当没有女医生时。”</p><p>她继续说道：“他们在第一次血管造影时错过了这一点，并认为我在假装。我最好的朋友说服他们给我第二个，他们发现我的出血已经流进了我的大脑，我的整个蛛网膜下腔，而且我的椎动脉破裂了。如果他们把我送回家，我就会死。 </p><figure id="attachment_3523734" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3523734" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3523734" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME.jpg" alt="莎朗·斯通" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sharon-Stone-article-NME-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3523734" class="wp-caption-text">莎朗·斯通——图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>“我的蛛网膜下腔（头部、颈部和脊柱）流了太多血，导致我的右脸摔倒，左脚严重拖拽，而且口吃得很厉害。”</p><p>斯通补充说，她现在必须每天服药，以解决这次经历带来的副作用，包括口吃和严重的脑部癫痫发作。</p><p>她解释说：“在最初的几年里，我的头顶上也会出现一些奇怪的指关节状的结，感觉就像被打了一拳……我无法表达这一切有多么痛苦。 ”</p><p>谈到她不愿透露自己病情的细节时，斯通继续说道：“我隐瞒了自己的残疾，不敢出门，不想让人们知道。我只是以为没有人会接受我。”</p><p>这位女演员此前透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-says-she-suffers-from-seizures-if-she-doesnt-get-eight-hours-of-sleep-a-night-3510055">，如果她因为这种情况每晚不能睡八小时，她就会患癫痫病。</a></p><p>斯通现在是美国巴罗神经学基金会的董事会成员，该基金会致力于治疗大脑和脊柱疾病。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-claims-doctors-thought-she-was-faking-brain-haemorrhage-3523615">莎朗·斯通声称医生认为她“假装”脑出血的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
