s/music/everything-everything-announce-new-album-mountainhead-and-2024-uk-tour-buy-tickets-preorder-3522070">此处的</a>日期。</p><p> 2024 年英国巡演门票将于格林威治标准时间下周五（11 月 3 日）上午 9 点开始发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Feverything-everything-tickets%2Fartist%2F72463" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。此外，预购新专辑的粉丝还可以获得预售票。现在<a href="https://everythingeverything.tmstor.es/?lf=1e5287636b83abe3023e7f6388833616" target="_blank" rel="noopener">就访问这里</a>进行操作。</p><p> 《Mountainhead》是该乐队继 2022 年 5 月发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/everything-everything-raw-data-feel-3227133">《Raw Data Feel》</a>之后一年多以来的首张新专辑。</p><p>请参阅下面的专辑封面和曲目列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3523556" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3523556" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3523556" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art.jpg" alt="一切一切“Mountainhead”专辑封面" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3523556" class="wp-caption-text">一切一切“Mountainhead”专辑封面。